new = '''The derivative identified the WSS original source, Bell’s sponsor event, the false service identities recorded at landlord and tenant control, local controller clock basis, session identifier `NB-WSS4-0708-2217`, device serial `SSO-NS-004`, full signer-state completion time, encrypted-block status, fields withheld, production authority, local seal reference, and proof ceiling. It did not identify Samuel Drennan as the WSS carrier.'''
